It is a free service and there are 
no copyright concerns. 
It has many users.

The quality is still a bit low, 
but it is expected that it will improve a lot in the near future.

You have to seize the 
opportunity when it comes. 
Now is the right time.

Understand trends and improve 
quality. Only then can we get 
out of the crisis.
